query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.score >= 10 AND q.score <= 1000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('clojure',
'express',
'flask',
'heroku',
'junit',
'kotlin',
'orm',
'recursion',
'sql-server-2005',
'vba',
'web-services',
'wordpress');
